    "For example, when investigating early childhood teachers' instructional activities, behavior, and emotions, Kurki and his colleagues (2016) delayed inviting teachers to take part in the interview by two weeks.",
    "Additionally, researchers argue that, apart from using generic questions, incorporating specific followup questions that closely align with the research aim is equally crucial (Heikonen et al., 2017; Hu and Wu, 2020).",
